&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-xl font-bold text-text-200 mt-1 -mb-0.5&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;whitespace-pre-wrap break-words&quot;&gt;We are seeking an experienced Concrete Carpenter to join our construction team. In this specialized role, you&#39;ll apply your expertise in building, erecting, and dismantling concrete forms, ensuring structural integrity and precise concrete placement according to project specifications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-xl font-bold text-text-200 mt-1 -mb-0.5&quot;&gt;Job Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
