&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Read and interpret blueprints, drawings, and specifications to determine dimensions and materials needed for concrete formwork&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Build, erect, install, and repair concrete forms and structures using wood, metal, or other materials&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Measure, cut, and shape wood, plastic, or other materials to create precise formwork for concrete pouring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Construct and set forms for foundations, walls, columns, stairs, and other concrete structures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Ensure proper alignment, leveling, and bracing of forms to meet specifications and ensure stability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Install expansion joints and embedded items in concrete structures as specified&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Strip and dismantle formwork after concrete has cured sufficiently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Maintain and care for equipment, tools, and materials used in concrete carpentry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Check completed formwork for quality, stability, and compliance with specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Apply curing compounds or perform other concrete finishing tasks as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Work collaboratively with concrete pouring teams and other construction trades&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-xl font-bold text-text-200 mt-1 -mb-0.5&quot;&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h2&gt;
