&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;2+ years of experience in concrete formwork and carpentry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Proven ability to read and interpret construction blueprints and specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Experience with various forming systems (including traditional wood forms and modular systems)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;whitespace-normal break-words&quot;&gt;Proficiency with carpentry tools and equipment specific to concrete work&lt;/li&gt;
