&lt;p&gt;Our Gulf Coast Industrial team is seeking experienced Pipefitter A’s and Pipefitter B’s to support our commercial and industrial project needs. Ideal candidates will demonstrate strong technical ability, reliability, and a commitment to safety and quality workmanship.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read and interpret isometrics, blueprints, and other construction drawings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate, request, and manage materials as needed for daily tasks&lt;/li&gt;
